{"article_id":"unuXlPWKSPbOMsTZ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Republican presidential candidate Ted Cruz won the endorsement of Wisconsin governor","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"- and former GOP rival -","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"Scott Walker Tuesday","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"as all five candidates converged on his state ahead of its key primary .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Walker said on Milwaukee conservative talk radio","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"that he was backing Cruz over Donald Trump and Ohio Gov . John Kasich","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"because he believes","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"the Texas senator is best positioned","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"to win the GOP nomination","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"and defeat presumed Democratic rival Hillary Clinton .","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"The endorsement comes","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"as Trump planned his first Wisconsin campaign stop in House Speaker Paul Ryan 's hometown .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"After the Janesville , Wisconsin , rally Trump was scheduled to join Kasich and Cruz for a CNN town hall in Milwaukee .","depth":4},{"id":13,"text":"In the increasingly contentious Democratic race , Vermont Sen. Bernie Sanders and Clinton were campaigning around the state .","depth":3},{"id":14,"text":"Walker , a two-term Republican","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"who became the first governor in U.S. history","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"to win a recall election in 2012 ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"had telegraphed his support for Cruz","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"after saying last week","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"he was the only candidate","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"who had a chance","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"to knock off Trump .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"When Walker ended his short-lived presidential campaign in September ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"he called for other candidates to join him","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"to make it easier to take out Trump .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"When Walker was running for president ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"he argued","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"a governor should be the nominee .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"But he passed over Kasich","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"to support Cruz ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"who until recently , had failed to garner the same level of support from the GOP establishment .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"`` It was an easy call for me to support Ted Cruz , ''","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Walker said ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"highlighting Cruz 's fights with both Republicans and Democrats .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"`` This is a guy","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"who has been consistent in his positions","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"when push comes to shove","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"will stand up for the people","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"he represents","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"over the interests in Washington . ''","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"Cruz supporters erupted in cheers","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"as Walker 's radio interview was played live at a rally outside of Milwaukee .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Trump made clear in a message","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"he posted Monday night","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"on Twitter","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that he was n't expecting to land Walker 's endorsement .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"`` After the way","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"I beat Gov . Scott Walker","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"( and Jeb , Rand , Marco and all others )","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"in the Presidential Primaries ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"no way","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"he would ever endorse me ! ''","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"Trump wrote ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"referring specifically to former contenders Jeb Bush and Marco Rubio .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"It 's unclear how much Walker 's endorsement will help Cruz ,","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"who has also won the backing of influential conservative talk radio hosts in the Milwaukee market","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"that reach into heavily Republican suburban counties .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"Walker 's approval rating has n't cracked 40 percent in more than a year .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"Wisconsin has 42 delegates ,","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"with 18 going to the statewide winner","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"and 24","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"divided up to the winner in each of the state 's eight congressional districts .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"Kasich has said","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"he hopes to win in a couple congressional districts ,","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"as Cruz and Trump battle it out","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"to win the state .","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"Kasich was campaigning for votes in suburban Milwaukee , as was Cruz","depth":4},{"id":68,"text":"who appeared with Carly Fiorina at a morning rally .","depth":4},{"id":69,"text":"On the Democratic side , Clinton was to appear at a gun violence forum in Milwaukee","depth":4},{"id":70,"text":"and then head north to Green Bay and west to La Crosse ,","depth":5},{"id":71,"text":"which is on the Minnesota border .","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"Sanders was stopping in the Milwaukee area and Appleton .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":145,"left":131,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":86,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":85,"right":13,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":84,"right":12,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":84,"left":82,"right":83,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":76,"right":81,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":75,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":74,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pa